metadata.name: The Magician
metadata.description:
Mercilessly foretelling, no lack of words for impetuous chatter. 
Ruling spirit of his body. 
Totalitarian adversary of any nefarious contract to decay. Manifestation of truth made law. Heavenly power brought to earthly cause. 

Owner of the sacred tongue, he works upon the elements.

With him, you will waver glory to the beat of his illusion, which will carry your light.
